&lt;p&gt;A video from the White House Correspondents' Association dinner has surfaced, showing the exact moment when US President Donald Trump was rushed out after a loud, unidentified ⁠noise was heard.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First Lady Melania Trump and other members of the Trump administration present at the dinner were also evacuated after a sudden commotion and loud noise erupted near the hotel ballroom where the event was underway.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
